msgctxt "sn45.90:0.2"
msgid "8. Dutiyaekadhammapeyyālavagga "
msgstr "8. Abbreviated Texts on One Thing "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.90:0.3"
msgid "90. Dutiyayonisomanasikārasampadāsutta "
msgstr "90. Accomplishment in Proper Attention (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.38, sc1
msgctxt "sn45.90:1.1"
msgid "“Yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, yonisomanasikārasampadā. "
msgstr "“… accomplishment in proper attention. "

msgctxt "sn45.90:1.2"
msgid "Yonisomanasikārasampannassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvessati, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarissati. "
msgstr "A mendicant accomplished in proper attention can expect to develop and cultivate the noble eightfold path. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.90:1.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yonisomanasikārasampanno ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant accomplished in proper attention develop and cultivate the noble eightfold path? "

msgctxt "sn45.90:1.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion, which culminate in the removal of greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn45.90:1.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yonisomanasikārasampanno ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant accomplished in proper attention develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.90:1.6"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.90:1.7"
msgid "Dutiyaekadhammapeyyālaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn45.90:2.1"
msgid "Kalyāṇamittaṃ sīlañca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.90:2.2"
msgid "chando ca attasampadā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.90:2.3"
msgid "Diṭṭhi ca appamādo ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.90:2.4"
msgid "yoniso bhavati sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
